  "description": "VMware ESXi host and vCenter Server SNMP trap monitoring. Maps the VMware enterprise (.1.3.6.1.4.1.6876) SNMP notifications for virtual machine power state changes (powered on/off, suspended), ESXi environmental and hardware alerts (hardware, chassis, thermal, disk, power supply, battery, processor, memory, BIOS) and vCenter Server alarm state changes to NetXMS events, and adds event-processing rules that raise alarms for them.",
